nter|19.0%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|117|582|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n| align=center|[[2005 Northern Ireland local elections|2005]]\n| align=center|121,991\n| align=center|17.4%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|101|582|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n| align=center|[[2011 Northern Ireland local elections|2011]]\n| align=center|99,325\n| align=center|15.0%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|87|583|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n| align=center|[[2014 Northern Ireland local elections|2014]]\n| align=center|85,237\n| align=center|13.6%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|66|462|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n| align=center|[[2019 Northern Ireland local elections|2019]]\n| align=center|81,419\n| align=center|12.0%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|59|462|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|}\n\n===European elections===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%\"\n|-\n!Election\n!First-preference vote\n!Vote %\n!Seats\n|-\n| align=center|[[1979 European Parliament election in the United Kingdom#Northern Ireland|1979]]\n| align=center|140,622\n| align=center|25.5%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|1|3|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n| align=center|[[1984 European Parliament election in the United Kingdom#Northern Ireland|1984]]\n| align=center|151,399\n| align=center|22.1%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|1|3|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n| align=center|[[1989 European Parliament election in the United Kingdom#Northern Ireland|1989]]\n| align=center|136,335\n| align=center|25.0%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|1|3|hex={{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n| align=center|[[1994 European Parliament election in the United Kingdom#Northern Ireland|1994]]\n| align=center|161,992\n| align=center|28.9%\n| align=left|{{Composition bar|1|3|hex={{Social De